'''Arallutes''' were flowers native to [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]. Trumpet-shaped, violet, and pungent, they were a rare weed from the [[Planet/Legends|world's]] plains. When they died, the petals would fold up and trap the seeds, which were then used as baby rattles. However, after the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destruction of Alderaan]] it took on new significance for the survivors. According to folklore, if a woman found one growing in her lawn, it meant that she would soon have a child. As a result, relatives of newlyweds would plant them in the couple's yard at night following the wedding; it was considered unlucky to get caught planting them.

